title: MUSIC VIDEO: Joe EL Feat. Iyanya - Chukwudi
content: Kennis Music Number One, Joe EL hits it harder with the beautiful visuals to his hit single Chukwudi featuring Iyanya. Chukwudi which is One of the songs off the Timeless Album which was released some months back. The video was directed by Clarence Peters. Watch, Enjoy and share your views.
